Bootstrap is a front-end framework --HTMLand CSS
It is providing you plug-ins for Javascript
It is providing design templates without javascripts plugins
Bootstrap for creating rsponsive pages.

Containers- require to wrap elements of a web site

2 types Containers classes provide by bootstarp--> 
.Container- provides a responsive fixed width container
.container-fluid--> provides full width conatiner, spanning entire width of a viewport


.container-sm small devices- screen width =>576 px
.container-md - >=768px
.container-lg >=992px
.container-xl >=1200px
.conatiner-xxl >=1400px

Bootstrap grid system
it divides width in 12 columns. the columns will re-arrange automatically depending on screen-size